<div class="team right-portion">
  <div class="title header-font" style="margin-top:20px;margin-left:20px;font-size: 25px;">Team</div>
  <div class="promo_text">

    <p style="font-size: 18px;line-height: 22px;">MyFabTab Inc. is a small (but beautifully formed) company based in the heart of Silicon Valley, California. Our
      mission is to provide you the best possible solution to manage all your offers, ads and other fab stuff
      all in one place. Currently FabTab is in Beta release which basically means we value your feedback on any
      little kinks you find. So if you want to know more about us, have a great idea for making
      FabTab even better, or just want to say hello, please contact us using the form below!</p>
    <br />
    <p style="font-size: 18px;line-height: 22px;">MyFabTab Inc. is self funded and always looking for world class talent to help us grow. So if you want to
      invest, have incredible skills or are a brand that wants to knows more, then please get in touch!</p>

  </div>

  <div  class="modal"  style=" margin-left: -269px;margin-top: 19px;position: relative;">
    <div class="modal-header">

      <h3>Contact Us</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body" style="padding:0px;margin-top:-24px;">
      <%= form_for @feedback, :url => {:action=>"promo_create", :controller=>"home" }, :method => :post do |form| %>

        <% if @feedback.errors.any? %>
          <% @feedback.errors.messages.each do |key,value| %>
            <% flash[:notice] = "#{key.capitalize}  #{value.join(',')}" %>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
        <fieldset>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 7px;float: left; margin-right: 46px;margin-top: 13px;">
            <label style="margin-right: 10px;"> From: </label>
            <%= text_field_tag :email, current_user.email, :readonly => true %>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 7px;float: left; margin-right: 122px;">
            <label style="margin-right: 10px;"> To: </label>
            <%= text_field_tag @email_to, @email_to ,:readonly => true %>
          </div>
          <div style="float: left;">
            <label style="margin-right: 10px;"> Message </label>
            <%= form.text_area :content, :rows => 5, :cols => 15 , :class => "text_width" %>
          </div>
        </fieldset>
        <fieldset>
          <%= form.submit "" ,:id => "invite" %>
        </fieldset>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .text_width
  {width: 300px;}
  #invite{
    border-radius: 12px 12px 12px 12px;
    height: 32px;
    margin-left: 242px;
    margin-top: -33px;
    width: 89px;
    background: url("/assets/btn_send.png");}
  .validation-error{
    display: none;
  }
</style>
<script type="text/javascript">
  $('.flash_messages1').fadeIn(2000).delay(5000).fadeOut(5000);
</script>



